                <p xml:id="KR3a0002-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-20a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-02-26T23:44:56.865+09:00">preparing written laws and orders</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-12T19:23:41.376+09:00">/頃 textologically uncertain/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-12T19:32:07.288+09:00">/政 most probably for 正/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-13T21:25:59.981+09:00">/the original 道  may be a better choice than the emendation 導/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-16T18:35:08.546+09:00">/the original 道  may be a better choice than the emendation 導/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_002-10a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T00:54:27.461+09:00">how would one know that the rituals are right?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_004-8a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T00:57:53.392+09:00">Given his behavour like a wild animal</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_004-8a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T00:59:49.615+09:00">and yet is desirous of others' trust in him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_004-8a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T01:00:42.411+09:00">and yet desires the affection of others.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_005-9a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T01:11:30.653+09:00">the true gentleman's measuring of himself is (as) with the (morall y objective) plumbline)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_005-11a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T01:13:01.073+09:00">the gentleman's practice of benevolence is never satisfied.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_006-12a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-20T01:16:41.327+09:00">like Heaven's embracing Heaven and Earth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-20T20:34:58.596+09:00">然后 should &gt; 然後</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-23T03:49:27.29+09:00">/textologically suspicious/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-23T03:50:39.005+09:00">/textologically suspicious/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-23T19:00:21.563+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-23T19:57:06.393+09:00">/以 obviously excrescent/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-23T20:28:40.23+09:00">/道 is emendation from 大/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-23T20:29:37.586+09:00">/textologically spurious/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-9a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-24T19:47:37.334+09:00">/霸 either excrescent, or the together with 主 the subject of the next sentence/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-14a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-30T02:59:26.49+09:00">/析 probably mistake for 折, 愿 possibly loan for 傆/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-05-30T16:30:29.287+09:00">/紫 probably mistake for 絺; 綌 itself emendation from 紶/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_008-13a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-30T21:53:48.134+09:00">衣食 is not a constituent. The relation of 衣 to 焉 is non-adjacent and therefore cannot be captured in the TLS syntactic categorisation.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_008-7a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-05-30T23:14:52.461+09:00">不可衣 but it could not be worn: probably passive here. We would expect 可以 in the active.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-20a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-03T15:58:50.627+09:00">/商 possibly a mistake for 章/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-20a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-07T04:50:46.136+09:00">/立器 unclear/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-20a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-07T16:03:23.093+09:00">/𧶜 is emendation for 賓; 𧵍 mistake for 貨/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-20a.96" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-07T16:42:22.54+09:00">/俗 = 欲/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-21a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-10T20:29:30.317+09:00">/捽 is already an emendation from 卒/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-21a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-09T16:56:22.052+09:00">/some take 所 and 誠 as belonging together; 愉殷 unclear/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-22a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-10T21:04:10.236+09:00">/忘 probably mistake for 妄/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-23a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-15T19:46:32.131+09:00">/之 mysterious to me (LZ)/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-23a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-16T04:22:42.598+09:00">/人 probably excrescent/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-23a.82" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2022-06-20T21:50:49.122+09:00">/為 enigmatic to me (LZ)/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-17T16:27:31.254+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-17T16:29:22.954+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-2a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-17T18:50:42.348+09:00">/不廢在王庭 absent from standard editions/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-17T20:07:58.219+09:00">/服 should probably be, on the basis of Yili, followed by 素積 as its object/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-5a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-23T21:01:27.02+09:00">/不 obviously excrescent/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-8a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-25T21:01:24.22+09:00">/天地  is emendation for 天下/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-10a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2023-05-29T03:30:47.179+09:00">/功 probably excrescent/</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_004-3a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-19T02:52:18.784+09:00">又＝猶</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_012-5a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-02T07:45:45.341+09:00">Is not that impossible/unfeasible?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_021-6a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-08T16:09:02.738+09:00">Only when in/with one's mind one knows the way</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_029-6a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-14T04:36:22.97+09:00">understands himself</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_029-6a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-14T04:36:46.289+09:00">takes good moral care of himself??</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_004-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-01T22:22:59.766+09:00">Very generally speaking, humans have things that unite them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_005-8a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-01T22:27:19.359+09:00">The 凡 is not necessarily just repeated in 莫不. 待考</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_013-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-01T22:30:59.171+09:00">人is not topicalised here. 凡 is adsentential.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_022-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-01T22:41:08.789+09:00">莫不 expresses descriptive generality, and 凡 espresses theoretical generalisation.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:56:49.51+09:00">Den Himmel groß zu machen (zu verehren) und über ihn nachzusinnen –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-11-07T21:53:44.453+09:00">ist das etwa so gut wie, die Nutztierhaltung praktizierend [vgl. 周易  /《序卦》:  物畜然後可養], ihn [d.h. seine Form und nicht seine Qualität auf den eigenen Bedarf] zuzuschneiden?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:57:07.521+09:00">Dem Himmel zu dienen und ihn zu preisen –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-11-07T18:25:44.04+09:00">ist das etwa so gut wie, das Mandat des Himmels [auf den eigenen Bedarf] zuschneidend, ihn zu nutzen?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:57:23.146+09:00">Nach einer (günstigen) Zeit Ausschau zu halten und auf sie zu warten –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:50:57.108+09:00">ist das etwa so gut wie, den Zeiten entsprechend, sich ihrer zu bedienen?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:57:31.542+09:00">Sich auf die Kreaturen zu stützen und sie sich mehren zu lassen –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:51:12.283+09:00">ist das etwa so gut wie, ihren Fähigkeiten freien Lauf lassend, sie zu verwandeln?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:57:41.211+09:00">Über die Kreaturen nachzusinnen und sie als Kreaturen zu behandeln –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-10-31T19:53:51.729+09:00">ist das etwa so gut wie die Kreaturen zu ordnen, auf dass man ihrer nicht verlustig gehe?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-11-07T18:46:36.615+09:00">Auf das zu hoffen, wodurch die Kreaturen entstehen,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-11-07T18:46:46.744+09:00">ist das etwa so gut wie das zu haben, wodurch die Kreaturen vollendet werden?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-11-07T19:23:29.497+09:00">Daher: Wenn man den Menschen beiseitelässt (sich vom Menschen abwendet?) und über den Himmel nachsinnt,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_017-13a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2023-11-07T19:00:18.465+09:00">so geht man der Disposition aller Kreaturen verlustig.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-13a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-11-09T09:39:58.024+09:00">As for pronunciations, as a matter of principle those that are not elegant pronunciations are to be discarded.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-24T17:12:49.41+09:00">the people of those others</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_009-8a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-24T17:13:25.562+09:00">the people of those others</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:35:41.219+09:00">勤屬: in other editions 勤厲 or 勤勵</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-13a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:37:35.195+09:00">矣 missing in at least some other editions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-13a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:39:54.997+09:00">雖欲無 attested many times as well as 雖欲毋: 無 is obviously an injuctive negative here, not a negative existential verb   Nab</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-15a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:47:50.968+09:00">note the change from 之 (*tə) to 者 (*tAɁ) in parallel sentences: more possible explanations; 利 might mean 'profitability', but I prefer 'profit' because of the parallel 功 (though this might mean 'effectiveness' instead of the common 'achievement' as well!)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-15a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:43:14.811+09:00">取天下者也 in some other editions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-15a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:43:35.58+09:00">保社稷者也 in some other editions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-15a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T17:43:52.39+09:00">危國家者也 in some other editions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-15a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-11T17:39:49.158+09:00">on the basis of parallelism, 於 obviously missing after 其 (see below 其於禮義節奏也!)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-15a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-10-03T18:23:06.459+09:00">須 possibly mistake for 順 standing for 慎</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-17a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-16T00:13:34.836+09:00">and in all the world there were none left who had a fresh complexion (being dessicated, all of them).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-17a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-11-19T18:21:18.094+09:00">Zhang Jue has 貪 instead of 貧</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_010-19a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#zadrapa" modified="2024-11-20T17:51:25.082+09:00">some have 順 instead of 煩</seg>
                </p>
